title: 175: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (August '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (August '22 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey did quite a haul and tried some great stuff, like gluten-free pepperoni pizza, dill pickle falafel bites, watermelon & peach macarons, peanut butter popcorn, a blueberry dessert bar, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a fruit spread that is TO DIE FOR! So don’t wait any longer—push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We went back to Trader Joe’s and taste-tested 16 things! Some were AMAZING, but some were just okay… Tune in to find out which is which!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
